<span class=3D"mw-editsection"><span class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">[</sp=
an><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=3DCovariance&amp;a=
ction=3Dedit&amp;section=3D1" title=3D"Edit section: Definition"><span>edit=
</span></a><span class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></div>
<p>For two <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Joint_distribution" cla=
